<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4316855>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 4. Height/length scatter plots of species from borehole 817 Lebăda Vest, drill core CM31, western portion of Black Sea shelf, Rhaetian, Late Triassic. In all diagrams, the dimensions of right (stars) and left (circles) valves of complete carapaces are shown separately and circled or linked. A. Pseudomacrocypris? kerabani Forel sp. nov. B. Hungarella koessenensis (Mette & Mohtat-Aghai, 1999)." ;
